rows.label: qst300407_msg0001
rows.name:
What business does an outsider
have in a place like this?

rows.label: qst300407_msg0002
rows.name:
Something entrusted by
a Gulan mercenary?

rows.label: qst300407_msg0003
rows.name:
Ah, Captain Saffran received
something from a Gulan as a
delivery to the homeland.

rows.label: qst300407_msg0004
rows.name: I do not know what it is...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst300407_msg0005
rows.name:
And even if I did, what good would
it do you if you cannot leave here?
